El Morado Natural Monument is a Chilean Natural Monument located in the Cajn del Maipo, Santiago Metropolitan Region. The monument is a glacial cirque and is part of the El Volcn River basin. Cerro El Morado dominates the landscape of this protected area. It is home to the San Francisco Glacier.

